FaceBase
~~~~~~~~

FaceBase is a resource for the craniofacial researchers.

System Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

You must have ERMREST installed on CentOS 6. 
 
Installation
~~~~~~~~~~~~

To install from the Subversion repository:

  1. From a source directory run:
     svn co https://svn2.misd.isi.edu/repos/tagfiler/facebase/trunk facebase

  2. From the source directory run the following command as root:
     rsync -av --delete --exclude=".*" --exclude="README" facebase /var/www/html/

Accessing the Application
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  1. In a browser type the following URL by replacing <hostname> with the one you have the installation:
     http://<hostname>/facebase

